  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "66593577b9f899001c2fa20f",
      "text": "Philosophy of tiddlers",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122446,
      "updated": 1717122446
    },
    {
      "id": "6659358dc9ec6a00009bdaf6",
      "text": "[TiddlyWiki]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122446,
      "updated": 1717122449
    },
    {
      "id": "6659359fc9ec6a00009bdaf8",
      "text": "[via: TiddlyWiki — a non-linear personal web notebook https://tiddlywiki.com/#Philosophy%20of%20Tiddlers]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122464,
      "updated": 1717122464
    },
    {
      "id": "665935e0c9ec6a00009bdaf9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122529,
      "updated": 1717122529
    },
    {
      "id": "665935e0c9ec6a00009bdafa",
      "text": ">The purpose of recording and organising information is so that it can be used again. The value of recorded information is directly proportional to the ease with which it can be re-used.",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122529,
      "updated": 1717122530
    },
    {
      "id": "665935e2c9ec6a00009bdafb",
      "text": "> The philosophy of tiddlers is that we maximise the possibilities for re-use by slicing information up into the smallest semantically meaningful units with rich modelling of relationships between them. Then we use aggregation and composition to weave the fragments together to present narrative stories.",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122530,
      "updated": 1717122530
    },
    {
      "id": "665935e2c9ec6a00009bdafc",
      "text": "> TiddlyWiki aspires to provide an algebra for tiddlers, a concise way of expressing and exploring the relationships between items of information.",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122530,
      "updated": 1717122530
    },
    {
      "id": "665935fbc9ec6a00009bdb02",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122555,
      "updated": 1717122555
    },
    {
      "id": "665935e3c9ec6a00009bdafd",
      "text": "[GPT-4o.icon]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122532,
      "updated": 1717122552
    },
    {
      "id": "665935e4c9ec6a00009bdafe",
      "text": ">情報を記録し整理する目的は、それを再利用できるようにすることです。記録された情報の価値は、それが再利用できる容易さに比例します。",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122532,
      "updated": 1717122542
    },
    {
      "id": "665935edc9ec6a00009bdaff",
      "text": "> ティドラーの哲学は、情報を意味的に最小限の単位に分割し、それらの間の関係を豊かにモデル化することで、再利用の可能性を最大化することです。その後、これらの断片を集約し、組み合わせて物語を構築します。",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122542,
      "updated": 1717122542
    },
    {
      "id": "665935edc9ec6a00009bdb00",
      "text": "> TiddlyWikiは、ティドラーの代数学を提供することを目指しています。これは、情報項目間の関係を簡潔に表現し探索する方法です。",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122542,
      "updated": 1717122542
    },
    {
      "id": "6659358ec9ec6a00009bdaf7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1717122446,
      "updated": 1717122446
    },
    {
      "id": "6659414aa56fda0000acb824",
      "text": " Cosenseにおいても[ページの分け方]とかの参考になると思う[seibe.icon]",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1717125451,
      "updated": 1717125504
    },
    {
      "id": "66594182a56fda0000acb826",
      "text": "  TiddlyWikiはtiddler群が上下に並ぶからより小さくてもいいから「意味的に最小限の単位」となっているけどCosenseではもう少し大きくても良いと思う",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1717125506,
      "updated": 1717125599
    },
    {
      "id": "665941e2a56fda0000acb827",
      "text": "   まあTiddlyWikiの公式ページを見ても結構長大なページもよくあるが…",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1717125603,
      "updated": 1717125735
    },
